[{'recipients': ['AUT'], 'body': 'Austria, let us be direct about the current situation. You hold TRI, I hold VEN - we are at a standoff that benefits neither of us while Russia and Turkey grow stronger. I propose a genuine working arrangement: I will move A VEN to TYR (away from TRI) and F ION toward the eastern Mediterranean to pressure Turkey. In return, I ask that you keep F AEG away from the Ionian and focus your forces on the Balkans against Turkey and Russia. Greece is a point of contention - I suggest we discuss a division of spoils in the east rather than fighting each other. What are your intentions this spring?'}, {'recipients': ['TUR'], 'body': "Turkey, the time for coordination is now. Austria holds GRE and AEG with their fleet - this blocks both of us. I propose: I move F ION to GRE this spring, taking it from Austria. You push A CON or A SER to support pressure on Austria's Balkan position. Austria is weakened with Russia holding BUD - this is the moment to strike. If we coordinate now, we can carve up Austria's Balkan centers between us. I take GRE, you take BUL/SER. Respond with your specific moves so we can synchronize."}, {'recipients': ['FRA'], 'body': "France, Austria retook TRI and now holds GRE and AEG - they are recovering dangerously. I intend to move F ION to GRE this spring to strike at Austria's Mediterranean position. I need you to confirm you will maintain pressure on Austria from the west - specifically, can you threaten MUN or push toward VIE? If Austria must defend on two fronts simultaneously, we both benefit. I am also watching Russia's growing strength - 6 centers is alarming. What is your strategic focus this year?"}]
--------------
FRA
[{'recipients': ['ENG'], 'body': "England, France has seized KIE and holds it now. Germany is squeezed between us - they have HOL, BEL, DEN, BER, MUN but KIE is mine. I propose we coordinate to finish Germany off: I push A KIE to BER while you press from BEL toward RUH or HOL. If we split Germany's centers - you take HOL and DEN, I take BER and MUN - we eliminate them as a threat entirely. My F WES can move to MAO to keep the Atlantic clear and signal I have no designs on your home centers. What say you? Let's divide Germany now while we have the advantage."}, {'recipients': ['GER'], 'body': 'Germany, France holds KIE. You have HOL, BEL, DEN, BER, MUN - five centers to my six. England is pressing you from BEL. I am pressing from KIE. You are surrounded. I offer you this: stand down and cede BER to France peacefully, and I will support you in holding HOL and DEN against England. Fight on two fronts and you will be eliminated within two years. The choice is yours - negotiate now or be crushed between France and England.'}, {'recipients': ['ITA'], 'body': 'Italy, France continues to expand northward into Germany. I hold KIE and am pushing toward BER. I have no interest in the Mediterranean or Italian sphere - my F WES will stay out of Tyrrhenian as promised. I encourage you to press Austria hard from VEN - take TRI and VIE while Austria is distracted by Turkey and Russia. A weakened Austria benefits us both. Keep me informed of your plans and I will do the same.'}]
