GER
[{'recipients': ['ENG'], 'body': "Confirmed - A BEL is moving to BUR this turn, clearing the path for F NTH to take BEL. A HOL moves to RUH to press toward MUN. Your F ENG pressuring France's Atlantic flank is exactly what we need. France is at 6 centers and must be cut down - you take BEL, I retake MUN, and we split France between us. Execute your moves and let's end French dominance this season."}, {'recipients': ['RUS'], 'body': "Agreed on all counts - non-aggression holds firm, I will not contest SWE and ask only that SIL and PRU remain clear. France's response to my ultimatum was to demand I cede BER - an insult that confirms they must be destroyed. I am executing A BEL-BUR and A HOL-RUH this turn to begin the reconquest of MUN. Your support in the east by keeping pressure on Austria and Turkey is the best contribution you can make to the overall balance. Our arrangement remains solid."}, {'recipients': ['FRA'], 'body': "Your offer to 'support me in holding HOL and DEN' in exchange for BER is laughable - you are asking me to surrender my home capital to avoid a fight you cannot win. England is taking BEL, I am driving into BUR and RUH, and you hold KIE with a single army that is already surrounded. You have one season to withdraw from KIE and MUN before you are dismembered. I am not negotiating the terms of my own destruction."}]
