[{'recipients': ['ENG'], 'body': "England, here are my specific intentions: A KIE moves to BER this spring, striking at Germany's heartland. F WES moves to MAO, keeping the Atlantic clear and signaling no threat to your home centers. A SPA holds to consolidate Iberia. I want you to press A BEL toward RUH or support into HOL - squeeze Germany from the west while I drive from the east. You take HOL and DEN, I take BER and MUN. Germany is finished within two seasons if we coordinate now. This is a genuine offer - France has no interest in fighting England when Germany is the common enemy between us."}, {'recipients': ['GER'], 'body': 'Germany, your threats are noted but your position is hopeless - England presses from BEL, France holds KIE and moves on BER. You cannot fight both of us simultaneously. I am moving A KIE to BER this turn. If you wish to survive in any form, your only option is to negotiate with me NOW: offer me BER and MUN, and I will advocate to England that you keep HOL and DEN as a rump state. Refuse, and you are eliminated within the year. The clock is ticking.'}, {'recipients': ['ITA'], 'body': "Italy, my focus this year is eliminating Germany - A KIE pushes to BER, which will give France 7 centers and decisive momentum. I cannot directly threaten VIE from my current position, but a weakened Germany means France can eventually push east. Press Austria hard from VEN - take TRI and push toward VIE. If Austria collapses, we both benefit enormously. Russia's 6 centers concern me too - once Germany is dealt with, we should discuss coordinating against Russian expansion in the Balkans. Keep F ION pressing Austria's Mediterranean flank."}]
